maintext:
Winning numbers drawn in ‘Georgia FIVE Midday’ game
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Georgia FIVE Midday” game were:
7-8-4-3-4
(seven, eight, four, three, four)
